<li>Your arms should be by your sides. Your head should be neutral and looking forward.</li>



<li>Inhale and engage your core. Exhale and raise your legs while keeping them straight. Your feet should stay together.</li>



<li>Pause briefly as your legs come to the top range of motion. Your lower back should stay firmly against the ground.</li>



<li>Inhale and lower your legs back to the starting position under control.</li>
